{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You've arrived at a mysterious island, where you take on the appearance of a child!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There is no grueling work here. All you need to do is to live happily, ever, after\u2026 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">When you've  grown tired of this life, however, could you find your way out?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">ABOUT THIS GAME</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Welcome to Neverland! In this game, you are the latest resident to join Neverland, an island offering a relaxing, joyful life for all.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As a resident of this island, you could:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147690/extras/QQ20241118-193400.png?t=1736647113\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00b7Explore its many locations:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147690/extras/QQ20241118-193422.png?t=1736647113\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00b7Socialize with NPCs rich in personalities, and - if situation allows - start a relationship with them!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147690/extras/QQ20241118-193446.png?t=1736647113\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00b7Plant crops and enjoy the harvest\uff1a</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147690/extras/QQ20241118-193311.png?t=1736647113\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00b7Make gourmet delights and treat your friends to a feast</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147690/extras/QQ20241118-193334.png?t=1736647113\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00b7Join holiday celebrations and collect festive awards</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147690/extras/QQ20241118-193235.png?t=1736647113\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00b7Find your way out of the island through exploration and deduction - the Grand Finale awaits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">And the island holds many more secrets for you to uncover\u2026</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Welcome!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3147690/9c319c478cba6393a7115a5408e9fcee3c59d31e.jpg"},{"name":"The exit, finally!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3147690/9fb333ace0e22774d1ac76074a0d85e58f8a586b.jpg"},{"name":"Bountiful Dive","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3147690/0b85a67f67c9f02045d18267f92b6c3f563a0a8e.jpg"},{"name":"Is this even readable?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3147690/3e8084fc739f3d12b3f87fe97a3e3383ae8f7528.jpg"},{"name":"Sacred Revelation","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3147690/f0115960fe1a5469218076835f68f5080a77fc1f.jpg"},{"name":"Jack and the Beanstalk","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3147690/61af1192c5f8cf1837bab1c74afb768f6084f437.jpg"},{"name":"Big boy!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3147690/19ca136674cb2e4c24b473a14a70a410608a4dd1.jpg"},{"name":"Open Sesame","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommu